data.reasoningText:
All 213 tests pass! But there's an unhandled error: `ResizeObserver is not defined`. This is thrown when pressing Escape on the combobox (which calls `closeCombobox` internally, which uses `ResizeObserver` for element movement detection).

The `ComboboxInput.test.tsx` already has a `ResizeObserver` mock:
```javascript
beforeAll(() => {
  globalThis.ResizeObserver ??= class ResizeObserver {
    observe() {}
    unobserve() {}
    disconnect() {}
  } as unknown as typeof globalThis.ResizeObserver;


});
```

I need to add the same mock to `SessionForm.test.tsx` to suppress this unhandled error and keep the tests clean.

